{"tid":711112,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"求耳機好介紹 (耳機大佬快啲入黎幫下小弟","createTime":"2018-06-21T09:37:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-24T05:24:18.000Z","uid":152048,"like":2,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"2debafca3343c565540499b085a40f1ffc935284","tid":711112,"uid":152048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T09:37:27.000Z","msg":"動漫撚嘅我聽咗日文歌好耐啦<br />\n想買個好啲嘅耳機聽歌<br />\n平時聽開:<br />\nLiSA<br />\nAimer<br />\n初音 (Keeno<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> , Narry<br />\n<del>各大聲優蘿莉聲系列</del><br />\n動漫歌(男女都有)<br />\n鹿乃<br />\n鎖那<br />\nかぴ<br />\nlefty hand cream<br />\n茶太<br />\n花姐<br />\n<br />\n除咗呢啲仲有好多純音樂例如東方嗰啲同人音樂<br />\n<br />\n求各位耳機大佬畀啲意見同選擇細佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n(其實好似全部女聲咁係咪應該買個女毒耳機?)<br />\n<br />\n(可能有啲人唔知嗰堆歌手係咩春<br />\n咁我就講下我聽嘅係咩類別<br />\n女聲為多<br />\n有啲都好rock 結他呀嗰啲<br />\n有啲好似香港AGA咁抒情<br />\n初音我都唔知點形容了 (電音?    )"},{"pid":"4904ce7085fbff24e891d02f546dedcba730ea7e","tid":711112,"uid":152048,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T09:38:29.000Z","msg":"我buget 大約二千"},{"pid":"6346636db140f19eb84570e7d78aa76524fa0fed","tid":711112,"uid":55190,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T09:39:24.000Z","msg":"波SIR <br />\n耳機界一哥"},{"pid":"c89371ecad87498607187b00a457ed73c25b68b0","tid":711112,"uid":1384,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T09:39:43.000Z","msg":"LCD3"},{"pid":"9684dacf7745a69a1272cacd382526f93c4a6e8a","tid":711112,"uid":34293,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T09:39:48.000Z","msg":"ath msr7"},{"pid":"56c6dabe5d5236f01262d0b0bc29f12324d8be40","tid":711112,"uid":8307,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-